desc: In a factory building, a man whistles and walks with an iron bar, and a man comes up in the distance with a flashlight.

A woman wearing a hat and a black dress skateboard outside, the woman jumped on the skateboard and fell to the ground. The picture turns, the woman successfully stands on the skateboard after jumping on the skateboard, the woman makes a whiny sound.
The fingers are pressed constantly on the piano keyboard, and the piano makes a corresponding melodious sound.
A color background picture with amplitudes and notes slowly disappears into a black, whistling sound.
A large white wind indicator whirled in the wind, rustling leaves around it.
In the wild, a wind bell hung under a tree, and the wind shook it back and forth, making a crisp ringing sound.
As the man's voice goes, a picture full of words is magnified, followed by multiple people shooting arrows.
A man in a black shirt struck a yellow tubular instrument with a black hammer in a yellow wall hall, while a group of people dressed in black played different instruments to the music.
To the music, a man in a plaid played a black instrument.
A clock hung on the wall of the room, and the gears kept turning to make beautiful music.
A woman starts clicking on her keyboard when she sees someone leaving, then pushes the monitor off the table and breaks it, breaking the glass in the background with laughter.
Inside the room, the craftsman was grinding a nail with tools, making a harsh sound.
To the music, a school of fish swam through the seaweed and down the sea floor.
Inside, a man was performing with a violin, and the sound of music was heard.
There was a deer's head on the wall of the room, and a blue bird came out of the door below, ticking.
Pictures of horses appear in the video, followed by the horse's hiss.
As the heart beats, the lines shrink and appear on a black background.
One person massages another person on the balcony following the sound of the lecture.
A man screwed a button and the spindle in the engine turned and squeaked.
A mouse squeaks on a running wheel in a cage.
On a table, a television set played the picture and made a prickly sound.
A band played instruments in the middle of the square, with the sounds of conversation among the people around it.
A black car pulled up in the open space in front of the white house, making the sound of its engine.
A man was on the stage banging on the instrument, the sound of which echoed in the room.
A man sleeps with his mouth open and snores
Two animated characters accompany the music, playing games, with many cakes falling in the background.
Inside, the electronic chicks on the alarm clock start to move as the alarm clock rings.
A grayish-yellow cat squatted in a cage, making a low cry.
In the music, a phone with a broken screen appears.
On one road, with the rumbling of the engine, a man rode his bicycle and disappeared.
A man was cutting a white cloth with scissors at the table, which made a snort.
In a city, a monk was ringing a bell, making a clang.
As the music went on, a man covered his face with his hand, and the picture turned, a woman with a pair of ponytails tilted her head against the tree.
Video shows a person holding a spray in the middle of a musical sound and spraying paint on a rotating circular object.
On a piece of red cloth, a man shook his instrument, which rattled, and then took out a similar instrument.
Inside, with the sound of a grinder, a man with glasses sat in front of the grinder and was grinding with a file, which had been polished and to be polished, on the table beside him.
With the background music, two anime characters appear, and then the picture switches to some English letters.
With the sound of guitars, two toy cars with fireworks on top are setting off.

Outside, a man in a green jacket and black shorts sat on a bamboo stand, pedaling a water windmill with his legs, trickling out of the stream, and the woman next to him spoke to him, and the two talked happily.
The puppy squatted in the woods half a hill, turning and running when he heard a roar like a tiger.
Thunder rang, a man outside the dilapidated warehouse took a gun and shot at the man in the outpost tower, then banging again looking for someone else to target.
Several people stood on the stage, and the music sounded to the sound of speeches and screams.
A man on the white table reached out to tune the machine to music.
With the sound of the horn, two men happily take drinks on the road while talking.
A parrot was standing on the handrail of the indoor staircase singing in the mirror.
A man in a Blue Jacket works out in a park with a long whip in his hand and a crackling sound.
To the music, a woman danced on the stage, cheering from below.
Cartoons were playing on the screen, and a car drove up and banged Spider-Man away.
A woman lying on the sofa, a person came up to the woman farted and made a sound, the woman covered her head with a quilt.
On a white bed, a white doorbell and a white switch were placed, and the doorbell blinked and tinkled.
A dolphin emerges to the surface as the music sounds, before the camera turns to the mountain.
The white stripes flickered as the music went on.
The sky was clouded with lightning and thunder, and a ball of fire was strewn through it.
To the music, a man in white sat in a chair playing the piano.
In the room, a girl was lying on the bed, shaking, and a dog was barking.
A white hamster eats broccoli on the table, clattering and chattering in the background.
In the room, a person is practicing playing table tennis, the table tennis is played out bouncing on the board to make a rattle.
The gray-haired foreign man performed on stage with a microphone in his left hand and a harp in his right.
A man was playing an instrument and the music echoed outside.
A flock of poultry cackled as they searched for food on the open grass as the wind blew.
